              <li>• Sequence of returns risk can derail the plan in early retirement</li>
              <li>• Requires annual re-evaluation and willingness to adjust spending</li>
              <li>• Psychologically difficult for lifelong savers to spend aggressively</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
